Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.Resources

Class ShelfCollection

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.Resources.CollectionResources
it.polimi.ingsw.model.Resources.ShelfCollection
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<Resource>
public class ShelfCollection
extends CollectionResources
this class extends CollectionResources and represent a set of resources with only one type, called "a set of compatible resources"
